<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #607D8B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .meeting-info { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #607D8B; }
        .status { display: inline-block; padding: 5px 10px; background: #4CAF50; color: white; border-radius: 3px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Meeting Confirmation Notice</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>A new counseling session has been confirmed in the system.</p>

        <div class="meeting-info">
            <p><strong>Meeting ID:</strong> <%= meetingId %><br>
               <strong>Date:</strong> <%= meetingDate %><br>
               <strong>Time:</strong> <%= meetingTime %><br>
               <strong>Type:</strong> <%= meetingType %></p>
        </div>

        <p><span class="status">Status: Confirmed</span></p>

        <p>The system has:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Sent confirmation emails to both parties</li>
            <li>Scheduled reminder notifications</li>
            <% if (meetingType === 'virtual') { %>
                <li>Created secure virtual meeting room</li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>

        <p>No action is required from you at this time. You will be notified if there are any changes or issues.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>